# PDFs and other binary manuals are stored locally only.
# The home-audio repo is mirrored to PUBLIC github.com/duhnz20/home-audio,
# and redistributing manufacturer PDFs there is a copyright concern + bloats the repo.
# The manuals/ index (manuals.md + manuals/README.md) tracks WHICH manual goes where
# and links to the manufacturer's official PDF source.
manuals/*.pdf
manuals/*.PDF
manuals/*.zip
manuals/*.djvu
manuals/*.epub

# Allow the README and any non-binary index files
!manuals/README.md
!manuals/*.md

# Maintenance log kept locally only — too granular for public mirror
maintenance-log.md
